               <lb/> Μάρθον Μαγ<lb break="no"/>δίου, <choice><sic>ἀπωθα<lb break="no"/>νεῖν</sic><corr>ἀποθα<lb break="no"/>νεῖν</corr></choice>
               <choice><sic>μητὰ</sic><corr>μετὰ</corr></choice> κα<lb break="no"/>λοῦ <choice><sic>ὠνώμα<lb break="no"/>τος</sic><corr>ὀνόμα<lb break="no"/>τος</corr></choice>
               <lb/>
               <choice><sic>ὐτῶν</sic><corr>ἐτῶν</corr></choice>
